parameters.vote:
a factor with levels:
A, will abstain; 
N, will vote no (against Pinochet);
U, undecided;
Y, will vote yes (for Pinochet).

parameters.education:
A factor with levels (note: out of order):
P, Primary;
PS, Post-secondary;
S, Secondary.

parameters.sex:
A factor with levels:
F, female;
M, male.

parameters.region:
A factor with levels:
C, Central;
M, Metropolitan Santiago area;
N, North;
S, South;
SA, city of Santiago.
